      "content": "Contact cards represent people and organizations associated with a project — clients, opposing parties, witnesses, adjusters, experts, and third parties. The Contacts API exposes the global contact list as well as project-scoped contact attachments and roles.\n\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Filevine API Support",
